"use strict";(globalThis.webpackChunkkodi_website=globalThis.webpackChunkkodi_website||[]).push([[130],{7735(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"1-24-enter-new-year-2026","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/1-24-enter-new-year-2026","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/metro-evolved/tree/main/blog/1-24-enter-new-year-2026.md","source":"@site/blog/1-24-enter-new-year-2026.md","title":"January 24 - Enter New Year 2026","description":"Welcome to a fresh new year at Kodi Studios. As we step into 2026 with the full momentum of AI, we are excited to roll out updates across both https//metroevolved.com.","date":"2026-02-23T00:44:52.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"KodiStudios","permalink":"/blog/tags/kodi-studios"},{"inline":true,"label":"MetroEvolved","permalink":"/blog/tags/metro-evolved"},{"inline":true,"label":"Tonivo","permalink":"/blog/tags/tonivo"},{"inline":true,"label":"Picturethrill","permalink":"/blog/tags/picturethrill"}],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"1-24-enter-new-year-2026","title":"January 24 - Enter New Year 2026","authors":"nikoari","tags":["KodiStudios","MetroEvolved","Tonivo","Picturethrill"]},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"January 31 - New Nikolai Aristov Website","permalink":"/blog/1-31-new-nikolai-aristov-website"}},"content":"Welcome to a fresh new year at Kodi Studios. As we step into 2026 with the full momentum of AI, we are excited to roll out updates across both https://kodistudios.com and https://metroevolved.com.\\r\\nThe latest version of the Tonivo App is now live, delivering even more value and delight for our users.\\r\\nWe\'re looking forward to a year of amazing websites and inspiring apps.\\r\\nHere\'s to making 2026 a memorable year along with our users and community.\\r\\n\\r\\n# Accomplishments\\r\\n\\r\\n## Kodi Studios Website\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Fixes  \\r\\n  Fixed Edit Links\\r\\n  Fixed DNS\\r\\n  Fixe Yaml Publish Pipeline\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\udcc8 Updates  \\r\\n  Updated Kodi Studios Website to latest packages, including Docusaurus V3, TypeScript, Node.js, Yarn V4 etc.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Metro Evolved Website\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f New Logo  \\r\\n  Created New Logo for MetroEvolved website\\r\\n\\r\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\r\\n\\r\\n* \u26f5 New Content Entries  \\r\\n  Added Entries for DNS and Apple Magic Mouse on Windows\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Fixes  \\r\\n  Fixed Website Layout\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\udcc8 Updates  \\r\\n  Updated Kodi Studios Website to latest packages, including Docusaurus V3, TypeScript, Node.js, Yarn V4 etc.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Tonivo App\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\udc23 New Tonivo App Version  \\r\\n  Released new version of Tonivo Windows App and added download link to Kodi Studios website:  \\r\\n  [https://kodistudios.com/docs/tonivo](https://kodistudios.com/docs/tonivo)\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83c\udf88 Single Exe  \\r\\n  Created option for Single Exe in Tonivo App\\r\\n  Download it at:  \\r\\n  [Tonivo.Desktop.exe](https://github.com/KodiStudios/tonivo-release/releases/download/26.1.21/Tonivo.Desktop.exe)\\r\\n\\r\\n# Next Effort\\r\\n\\r\\n## Picturethrill App\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\udc23 New Picturethrill App Version  \\r\\n  Release to Kodi Studios Website\\r\\n\\r\\n* \ud83d\udcc8 Updates  \\r\\n\\r\\n  Update Picturethrill App to 2026"},{"id":"1-31-new-nikolai-aristov-website","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/1-31-new-nikolai-aristov-website","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/metro-evolved/tree/main/blog/1-31-new-personal-website.md","source":"@site/blog/1-31-new-personal-website.md","title":"January 31 - New Nikolai Aristov Website","description":"Lots of great progress around Kodi Studios.","date":"2026-02-23T00:44:52.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"KodiStudios","permalink":"/blog/tags/kodi-studios"},{"inline":true,"label":"MetroEvolved","permalink":"/blog/tags/metro-evolved"},{"inline":true,"label":"Tonivo","permalink":"/blog/tags/tonivo"},{"inline":true,"label":"Picturethrill","permalink":"/blog/tags/picturethrill"}],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"1-31-new-nikolai-aristov-website","title":"January 31 - New Nikolai Aristov Website","authors":"nikoari","tags":["KodiStudios","MetroEvolved","Tonivo","Picturethrill"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"January 24 - Enter New Year 2026","permalink":"/blog/1-24-enter-new-year-2026"},"nextItem":{"title":"February 16 - Upload New Images","permalink":"/blog/2-16-upload-new-images"}},"content":"Lots of great progress around Kodi Studios.\\r\\nRecently, created new lifestyle personal website:  \\r\\nhttps://nikolaiaristov.com\\r\\n\\r\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\r\\n\\r\\n# Accomplishments\\r\\n\\r\\n## Metro Evolved Website\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Updated Docusaurus Instructions  \\r\\n  As part of creation of new website https://nikolaiaristov.com, also updated\\r\\n  instructions on Docusaurus:  \\r\\n  https://metroevolved.com/docs/category/create-site\\r\\n  Now it\'s easier more than ever to create\\r\\n  low-cost websites\\r\\n\\r\\n## Tonivo App\\r\\n\\r\\nhttps://kodistudios.com/docs/tonivo\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\udc23 Enabled Tonivo App on Lower Windows Versions\\r\\n  Originally, Tonivo App was able to run\\r\\n  only on most recent Windows.\\r\\n  However, it would be nice to support to more\\r\\n  Windows versions, including some older ones.\\r\\n  This really increases users who can download and use\\r\\n  Tonivo App. Now, all of the following versions are supported:\\r\\n  - Windows 11\\r\\n  - Windows 10\\r\\n  - Windows 8\\r\\n  - Windows 7\\r\\n\\r\\n# Next Effort\\r\\n\\r\\n## Picturethrill App\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\udc23 New Picturethrill App Version  \\r\\n  Release to Kodi Studios Website\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Updates  \\r\\n  Update Picturethrill App to 2026\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:\\r\\n  https://nikolaiaristov.com"},{"id":"2-16-upload-new-images","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2-16-upload-new-images","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/metro-evolved/tree/main/blog/2-16-upload-new-images-decisions.md","source":"@site/blog/2-16-upload-new-images-decisions.md","title":"February 16 - Upload New Images","description":"It turns out that OneDrive is rather slow to display images through shared URLs.","date":"2026-02-23T00:44:52.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"KodiStudios","permalink":"/blog/tags/kodi-studios"},{"inline":true,"label":"MetroEvolved","permalink":"/blog/tags/metro-evolved"},{"inline":true,"label":"Tonivo","permalink":"/blog/tags/tonivo"},{"inline":true,"label":"Picturethrill","permalink":"/blog/tags/picturethrill"}],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"2-16-upload-new-images","title":"February 16 - Upload New Images","authors":"nikoari","tags":["KodiStudios","MetroEvolved","Tonivo","Picturethrill"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"January 31 - New Nikolai Aristov Website","permalink":"/blog/1-31-new-nikolai-aristov-website"},"nextItem":{"title":"February 22 - Switch Images to Claudinary","permalink":"/blog/2-22-switch-to-claudinary"}},"content":"It turns out that OneDrive is rather slow to display images through shared URLs.\\r\\nThus, I ventured onto journey to find alternatives to OneDrive.\\r\\n\\r\\n# Accomplishments\\r\\n\\r\\n## Images Research\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Cloudify  \\r\\n  After real world testing of OneDrive as image provider\\r\\n  through URLs, it turned out that OneDrive is extremely slow.\\r\\n  Like it takes about 5 seconds to load a single image.\\r\\n  Started to explore other providers. One promising solution\\r\\n  is Cloudify.\\r\\n  However, during my research, I ran out of VsCode\\r\\n  Copilot Credits \ud83d\ude05\\r\\n  Which just shows how important AI utilities have\\r\\n  become nowadays.\\r\\n\\r\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\r\\n\\r\\n# Next Effort\\r\\n\\r\\n## Personal Site https://aristov.net\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:  \\r\\n  https://aristov.net"},{"id":"2-22-switch-to-claudinary","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2-22-switch-to-claudinary","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/metro-evolved/tree/main/blog/2-22-switch-to-cloudinary.md","source":"@site/blog/2-22-switch-to-cloudinary.md","title":"February 22 - Switch Images to Claudinary","description":"Finally found replacement of OneDrive with Claudinary.","date":"2026-02-23T00:44:52.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"KodiStudios","permalink":"/blog/tags/kodi-studios"},{"inline":true,"label":"MetroEvolved","permalink":"/blog/tags/metro-evolved"},{"inline":true,"label":"Tonivo","permalink":"/blog/tags/tonivo"},{"inline":true,"label":"Picturethrill","permalink":"/blog/tags/picturethrill"}],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"2-22-switch-to-claudinary","title":"February 22 - Switch Images to Claudinary","authors":"nikoari","tags":["KodiStudios","MetroEvolved","Tonivo","Picturethrill"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"February 16 - Upload New Images","permalink":"/blog/2-16-upload-new-images"},"nextItem":{"title":"February 7 - Update OneDrive Embed Project","permalink":"/blog/2-7-new-nikolai-aristov-website"}},"content":"Finally found replacement of OneDrive with Claudinary.\\r\\n\\r\\n# Accomplishments\\r\\n\\r\\n## Images Research\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Claudinary  \\r\\n  Created end-to-end Image solution for WebSites using Claudinary.\\r\\n  So far, I\'m impressed with Claudinary speed and ease of configuration.\\r\\n  Hopefully, it will be a nice solution for WebSite Images and other\\r\\n  assets.  \\r\\n  New Claudinary asset manager scripts are available at:  \\r\\n  https://github.com/KodiStudios/cloudinary-embed\\r\\n\\r\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\r\\n\\r\\n## Personal Site https://nikolaiaristov.com\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:  \\r\\n  https://nikolaiaristov.com\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\udcd6 Improved Getting Started Documentation  \\r\\n  Includes Development.md and ReadMe.md\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83c\udf09 Switched from PnP to Node Modules  \\r\\n  This will help with future project maintenance\\r\\n  Yarn V4 Node Modules makes it easier for\\r\\n  IDE Editors and other utilities to manage the project\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83c\udf07 Switched End Line setting  \\r\\n  Minor, but important so that repo can work well\\r\\n  on all platforms, including Windows and macOS\\r\\n\\r\\n# Next Effort\\r\\n\\r\\n## Personal Site https://aristov.net\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83c\udf88 Align DNS Settings  \\r\\n  Need to switch https://aristov.net to point to\\r\\n  https://nikolaiaristov.com  \\r\\n  This will allow full merge.  \\r\\n  Also, need to consider:  \\r\\n  https://aristov.eu"},{"id":"2-7-new-nikolai-aristov-website","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2-7-new-nikolai-aristov-website","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/metro-evolved/tree/main/blog/2-7-update-onedrive-embed.md","source":"@site/blog/2-7-update-onedrive-embed.md","title":"February 7 - Update OneDrive Embed Project","description":"Of course a nice website needs to have great content, not only","date":"2026-02-23T00:44:52.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"KodiStudios","permalink":"/blog/tags/kodi-studios"},{"inline":true,"label":"MetroEvolved","permalink":"/blog/tags/metro-evolved"},{"inline":true,"label":"Tonivo","permalink":"/blog/tags/tonivo"},{"inline":true,"label":"Picturethrill","permalink":"/blog/tags/picturethrill"}],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"2-7-new-nikolai-aristov-website","title":"February 7 - Update OneDrive Embed Project","authors":"nikoari","tags":["KodiStudios","MetroEvolved","Tonivo","Picturethrill"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"February 22 - Switch Images to Claudinary","permalink":"/blog/2-22-switch-to-claudinary"}},"content":"Of course a nice website needs to have great content, not only\\r\\ntext but pictures. For personal website https://nikolaiaristov.com\\r\\nthere needs to be a way to store pictures for it.\\r\\n\\r\\nOne of answers is OneDrive Embed Script.\\r\\nIt allows users to store pictures on OneDrive and then reference them\\r\\nfrom their website.\\r\\n\\r\\n# Accomplishments\\r\\n\\r\\n## OneDrive Embed Script\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Updated OneDrive Embed Project  \\r\\n  Tons of goodness, updated yarn, linting, TypeScript, testing  \\r\\n  Updated to use latest and greatest patterns  \\r\\n  Added OneDrive Api Integration test  \\r\\n  This allows to easily verify OneDrive Embed Script\\r\\n\\r\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\r\\n\\r\\n# Next Effort\\r\\n\\r\\n## Personal Site https://nikolaiaristov.com\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:\\r\\n  https://nikolaiaristov.com\\r\\n\\r\\n## Picturethrill App\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\udc23 New Picturethrill App Version  \\r\\n  Release to Kodi Studios Website\\r\\n\\r\\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Updates  \\r\\n  Update Picturethrill App to 2026"}]}}')}}]);